# Windsurf Rules for Javascript Project

## no-abbreviations

Avoid using abbreviations in code identifiers and comments. Use full, descriptive terms.
examples = Use `button` instead of `btn`, `container` instead of `cnt`, `navigation` instead of `nav`

---

